parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unwanted activation of the automatic emergency braking system can cause sudden stops, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and even fatalities, especially if other vehicles are following closely behind.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or slows down without any obstacles or vehicles in front
the dashboard flashes a "brake" warning
the vehicle comes to a complete stop or slows down rapidly
the driver experiences sudden jerking or jolting
and the vehicle may even cause accidents or near-misses.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brakes do not engage properly
the vehicle slows down but does not come to a complete stop
error messages appear on the dashboard
including "Brake System Problem"
"Tire Pressure Monitor Problem"
"Brake Hold System Problem"
and others.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses speed
all dash lights come on
a loud noise is heard
the vehicle shuts off
error messages appear on the dashboard
including "12 Volt Battery Charging System Problem"
"Power Reduced"
and others.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lane assistance system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The lane assistance system engages when there is no obstacle
the vehicle suddenly slows down or stops
error messages appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the display screen can cause the driver to lose important information, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The display screen goes blank
error messages appear on the dashboard
the screen flickers or becomes distorted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the pedals do not return to their normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sunroof can cause injury or distraction to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters or breaks
glass falls on the driver and passengers
the sunroof opens or closes unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Consumption and Oil Consumption Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive fuel and oil consumption can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive fuel
the oil consumption is too high
the vehicle requires frequent oil changes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
often when shifting gears or parking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injuries from flying glass and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters suddenly without warning
often with no apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the rear window can cause injuries from flying glass and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The rear window shatters suddenly without warning
often with no apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The air conditioner blows hot air
regardless of the temperature setting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the strut tower can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The strut tower comes apart suddenly
often with no apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the trunk can cause injuries from sudden closure and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The trunk does not open or close properly
often getting stuck or closing suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries due to underinflated tires.
symptoms: The TPMS fails to warn of low tire pressure in a timely manner.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the touch screen can cause distractions while driving and difficulties with navigation and entertainment.
symptoms: The touch screen goes black
fails to respond
or has connectivity issues with Apple CarPlay.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brake system activates suddenly without warning
often with no apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The headlights fail to provide adequate illumination
often with a band of darkness on the upper part of the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hood latch sensor can cause distractions while driving and difficulties with maintenance.
symptoms: The hood latch sensor beeps or vibrates without warning
often with no apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the keyless start system can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle can roll away without warning
even when turned off
due to the keyless start system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cabin heating system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The cabin heating system fails to warm up the cabin while idling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Bluetooth audio system can cause distractions while driving and difficulties with communication.
symptoms: The Bluetooth audio system produces background noise
often with no apparent cause.
